RF Planning Studio: Link Feasibility Assessment
Overview

This repository presents an assessment of a wireless RF communication link. By adjusting important design parameters within a MATLAB simulation, the resulting impact on coverage range, received signal level, and Fresnel zone clearance can be observed.

