1ï¸âƒ£ Increasing Gateway Height by +5 m

Does the maximum LOS distance change?
Yes. The maximum Line-of-Sight (LOS) distance increases from approximately 21.1 km to 23.2 km.

Does link feasibility improve noticeably?
From the perspective of the log-distance path loss model used in this analysis, the numerical improvement is small. However, in practical scenarios, increasing the antenna height leads to a clear improvement in physical link feasibility.

